### Step 2: Create Source Files (6 source files + 3 test files)

#### 2a. `packages/pixelart/src/version.ts`

Exact copy of `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775507088418-3a79wi/packages/prodia/src/version.ts`:
