#### 3b. `packages/pixelart/src/pixelart-provider.test.ts`

Model after `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775507088418-3a79wi/packages/prodia/src/prodia-provider.test.ts`:

