Design a detailed implementation plan for adding a new fictional "PixelArt" AI provider (`@ai-sdk/pixelart`) to the Vercel AI SDK. This provider ONLY supports image generation (no text, chat, embeddings). 

## Requirements
- Export a `createPixelArt` factory function and a default `pixelArt` singleton
- Support image settings: size, style ("pixel", "retro", "8bit"), and pixel density (number)
- Use "https://api.pixelart.ai/v1" as default base URL
- API key from `PIXELART_API_KEY` env variable
- Follow the exact same package structure as existing providers
- Do NOT modify any existing packages — only create new files under `packages/pixelart/`
